title: Namaskar Vegetarian Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Organic, Western, Take-out, Asian
description: This vegetarian cafe opened Sept 2014. Prepares food with mantra and love. Serves fried rolls, seaweed fritters, salads, pasta and more. Try the oregano juice. No alcohol. No smoking. Hosts yoga classes, sometimes live music. Walls adorned with artwork.
